name: The Perfect Couple Netflix
summary: "The Perfect Couple," a Netflix murder mystery, has received varying reactions. Some reviewers, like USA TODAY, have called it a "dumbed-down 'White Lotus'" due to its predictable plot and shallow characters. However, others, such as Harper's BAZAAR, appreciate its fan casting and gorgeous visuals. The Chicago Sun-Times describes it as a "gorgeous" and "set at a high-end wedding." Meanwhile, Vulture gives an in-depth recap of the series premiere, while IndieWire finds it "limited fun" despite Kidman's performance. CinemaBlend expresses excitement for the book adaptation, and Glamour praises the dance sequence. Variety lauds the show's "profoundly unserious" tone, while The Guardian deems it "ludicrously good." Overall, critics offer diverse perspectives on this Netflix mystery, ranging from negative to positive.

name: Daylight saving time
summary: Daylight Saving Time (DST) is ending, bringing an extra hour of sleep on November 5th. However, this time change is not observed in all US states. Arizona and Hawaii, along with most of the territories, do not participate in DST. There is ongoing discussion about permanently ending DST, but no action has been taken yet. Residents of states that do observe DST should prepare by setting their clocks back an hour before going to bed on November 4th. This time change applies to most states in the US, but there are exceptions, such as those mentioned above. More information about states that won't observe DST can be found in various articles, including those from IndyStar, NJ.com, NorthJersey.com, Oklahoman.com, NBC Chicago, PennLive, Black Enterprise, AS USA, and Tododisca.

name: Isaiah Likely
summary: Isaiah Likely, a tight end for the Baltimore Ravens, impressed in his NFL debut against the Kansas City Chiefs. Despite a narrow loss, Likely made a significant impact, showcasing his athleticism with an impressive juke and securing the game's longest touchdown. Despite an injury scare, he proved to be a reliable target for quarterback Lamar Jackson. Ravens GM Eric DeCosta believes that Likely and fellow tight end Mark Andrews will form the NFL's top tandem in 2024. Likely's journey from college to the NFL has been fueled by his platform-lifting experiences. Fantasy football analysts have praised Likely's Week 1 performance, predicting a strong season ahead.

name: Astro Bot
summary: The PlayStation 5 exclusive game "Astro Bot: Rescue Mission" has garnered widespread praise from critics, with multiple sources hailing it as a masterpiece and the best game of the year so far. Forbes calls it "the triumphant exclusive the PS5 desperately needed," while TheGamer declares it "not a museum" but a "masterpiece." GameSpot praises its immersive gameplay, saying "it's like flying to the moon," while IGN simply states it's an "all-time great." Kotaku describes the game as "a bountiful galaxy of bots," and Shacknews applauds its history-lesson-esque levels. CGMagazine notes its high replayability, and The New York Times commends its fun and educational elements. GAMINGbible summarizes the consensus by calling it "an all-time great of stratospheric proportions." Overall, these reviews suggest that "Astro Bot: Rescue Mission" is a must-play title for PlayStation 5 owners.
